# My Final Code

```java
static int maxProfit(int[] prices) {

    int minPrice = Integer.MAX_VALUE;
    int maxProfit = 0;

    for (int price : prices) {

        if (price < minPrice) {

            minPrice = price;

        } else {

            int profit = price - minPrice;
            maxProfit = Math.max(maxProfit, profit);

        }
    }

    return maxProfit;
}
```

